      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOB MENTALITY (6) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 2 lengths (18.51) behind Chattahooche at Wagga. Leading chance again. REBORN RUBY (2) turned in a moderate effort last time when sixth at this track over 330m behind My Rupee (19.47) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Form from her last run is proving strong. Leading chance. JACOBITE THORN (4) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, 0.8 lengths from the winner Lone Dazzler (19.00) at this track. Can measure up. MAGIC TECHNIQUE (1) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to turn the form around.",
